`break` exits the innermost loop immediately. `continue` skips to the
next iteration:

```mojo
for x in range(10):
    if x == 5:
        break        # Stop at 5
    if x % 2 == 0:
        continue     # Skip even numbers
    print(x)         # Prints 1, 3
